    ICommandStackListener, IDatelineModelListener, IPagingModelListener, IColumnModelListener, KeyListener, ImageObserver, LayoutManager, MenuContainer, Printable, PropertyChangeListener, Serializable, EventListener, Accessible

    public class PrintGanttChart
extends AbstractGanttChart
implements LayoutManager, Printable, IDatelineModelListener
    A Gantt chart specialized on being printed that takes another Gantt chart as its input and copies its configuration object. The Gantt chart does not have any scrollbars or splitter panels / handles that are not needed for printing.
    Since:
    1.0
    Version:
    $Revision: 1.9 $
    Author:
    Dirk Lemmermann

    • Method Detail

      • copySettings

        protected void copySettings(PrintContext ctx)
        Copies various settings from various Gantt chart UI components to the printable Gantt chart. This method needs to be called every time before bringing up the preview dialog as some settings might have changed since the last time the Gantt chart was printed.
        Parameters:
        ctx - the print context
        Since:
        1.0

      • copySettings

        protected void copySettings(PrintContext ctx,
                            boolean initialCopy)
        Copies various settings from various Gantt chart UI components to the printable Gantt chart. This method needs to be called every time before bringing up the preview dialog as some settings might have changed since the last time the Gantt chart was printed.
        Parameters:
        ctx - the print context
        initialCopy - a flag signalling whether this method gets called for the first time or for follow up print attempts (some settings might only need to be copied the first time around, after that the preview dialog will keep / manage the state of the printable Gantt)
        Since:
        1.1
